# id: SearchAfterSortedDocQuery -> static int searchAfterDoc(TopComparator comparator, int from, int to) throws IOException

codeText: static int searchAfterDoc(TopComparator comparator, int from, int to) throws IOException {_        int low = from__        int high = to - 1___        while (low <= high) {_            int mid = (low + high) >>> 1__            if (comparator.lessThanTop(mid)) {_                high = mid - 1__            } else {_                low = mid + 1__            }_        }_        return low__    }
